How to Use This Script

1. Install dependencies if you donâ€™t have them:

pip install opencv-python pytesseract openpyxl


2. Make sure you have Tesseract OCR installed and accessible in your system PATH.


3. Place your card images (front.jpg and back.jpg or rename as needed) in the script folder.


4. Edit the expected_info dictionary inside main() with the card details you want to verify.


5. Run the script. It will:

Create card_catalogue.xlsx if missing

Verify the card by OCR and text matching

Append the result to the Excel sheet automatically.
